    <div class="about-block">
    <div class="about-block-text">This Project was created as a part of a graduation project in communication design. It provides a tool that can be used to visualize music. The fusion between musical atmosphere, visual representation and figurative poetic language can be discovered and reinvented through improvisation and dialogue. The Glossary below shows theoretical research and content on the topic.</div>
